<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>관리 · 모임 테일보드</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="brand"><a href="/">모임 테일보드</a></div>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">공동체 선택</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>
  <main class="container container--wide">
    <h1>관리</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">이벤트와 옵션 그룹을 등록할 수 있습니다.</p>

    <div class="tenant-pills">
      <strong style="margin-right: 8px;">공동체:</strong>
      <a href="/t/<%= tenant.slug %>/events"><%= tenant.name %> 이벤트</a>
      <a href="/admin/tenants/<%= tenant.slug %>"><%= tenant.name %> 관리자</a>
    </div>
    <p class="page-subtitle" style="margin-top: -8px;"><strong>관리자</strong> 링크에서 해당 공동체의 관리자(사용자명)를 추가·삭제할 수 있습니다.</p>

    <div class="admin-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="card__title">이벤트 만들기</h2>
        <form method="post" action="/admin/events">
          <input type="hidden" name="tenantSlug" value="<%= tenant.slug %>" />
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="title">제목</label>
            <input id="title" name="title" required placeholder="예: 3/7 인천 수련회" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="description">설명 <span class="optional">(선택)</span></label>
            <textarea id="description" name="description" placeholder="이벤트 설명"></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="eventDate">일시</label>
            <input id="eventDate" name="eventDate" type="datetime-local" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>
              <input type="checkbox" name="isActive" value="true" checked />
              공개 (목록에 표시)
            </label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="adminUsername">관리자 사용자명 <span class="optional">(로그용)</span></label>
            <input id="adminUsername" name="username" placeholder="예: yuna9354" />
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn--primary" type="submit">이벤트 만들기</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="card__title">옵션 그룹 추가</h2>
        <form method="post" action="/admin/options">
          <input type="hidden" name="tenantSlug" value="<%= tenant.slug %>" />
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="eventId">이벤트 ID</label>
            <input id="eventId" name="eventId" type="number" required placeholder="숫자 입력" min="1" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="groupName">그룹 이름</label>
            <input id="groupName" name="groupName" required placeholder="예: 식사, 이동, 파트" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>
              <input type="checkbox" name="multipleSelect" value="true" />
              여러 개 선택 가능
            </label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="options">옵션 (한 줄에 하나)</label>
            <textarea id="options" name="options" placeholder="식사 O&#10;식사 X"></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="adminUsername2">관리자 사용자명 <span class="optional">(로그용)</span></label>
            <input id="adminUsername2" name="username" placeholder="예: yuna9354" />
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn--primary" type="submit">옵션 그룹 추가</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
